name: NFT House #1 - Full Model
description: (Perhaps?) the first house design minted on the Tezos blockchain. NFT House #1 is a design for an imaginary NFT collector who collects primarily clean NFTs and does not trade on the Ethereum chain. The owner of this NFT has full rights to this schematic design documentation including personal modification. These documents are not for construction, but can be further developed for construction through consultation with the original designers and engineers.
